ouncement, the new amount under the unemployment allowance scheme is Rs. 3500 for girls and Rs. 3000 for boys.To get more details and apply form PDF download, check Berojgari Bhatta Guidelines at this link or visit the official website http://www.employment.livelihoods.rajasthan.gov.in/  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}